{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e7c5142cff","title":"应以红一军团一部先占界石铺","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"94786de8ba","index":0,"year":1936,"month":9,"day":17,"articleId":"e7c5142cff"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-1","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(1)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"25753282bf","type":"paragraph","text":"应以红一军团一部先占界石铺","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"e7c5142cff"},{"id":"0469d0ba7f","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年9月17日）彭，并报是”","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"e7c5142cff"},{"id":"6cb38f4f74","type":"paragraph","text":"界石铺既无敌，一师应以一个团附骑兵一部在明日确实占领之，并向东南游击，以待四方面军来接替。否则胡宗南先占该地大为不利。另派一部直达隆德、静宁道上扰乱","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"e7c5142cff"},{"id":"cd66619935","type":"paragraph","text":"毛","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"e7c5142cff"},{"id":"adf6944b45","type":"paragraph","text":"十七日十五时半","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"e7c5142cff"},{"id":"98304c70e0","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]这是毛泽东给红军第一方面军司令员、西方野战军司令员兼政治委员彭德怀的电报。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"e7c5142cff"},{"id":"e94419d3c4","type":"paragraph","text":"[2]爱，指爱荣臻，当时任红军第一方面军第一军团政治委员，率该军团第一师前出静宁、隆德，策应红军第四方面军北上。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"e7c5142cff"},{"id":"c040e009c8","type":"paragraph","text":"[3]胡宗南，当时任国民党军西北“剩”总司令部第一军军长兼第一师师长。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"e7c5142cff"}],"page":{"id":"f1c203f717","publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"e7c5142cff","start":136,"end":136}}}},"__N_SSG":true}